                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5731" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0181</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7950 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">加加食品-控股股东资金占用何时休？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When will the problems of funds occupation of controlling shareholders of Jiajia Food Group Co., Ltd to end？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石善冲，闫艳敏，赵志刚，马岩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">加加食品集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">控股股东；资金占用；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Controlling Shareholders; Capital Occupation; Corporate Governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">加加食品是一家集生产、研发、销售于一体的大型调味食品企业，上市之前业绩稳步增长并一举成为中国调味品行业的第一家上市公司。然而，上市之后在实际控制人操纵下发生的控股股东资金占用事件，不仅导致企业业绩增长乏力，在调味品行业节节败退，还严重损害了企业形象，使公司多次受到证监会处罚，最终被实施其他风险警示。本案例以加加食品上市后发生的多起控股股东违规占用资金事件为主线，详细描述了控股股东侵占上市公司利益的动因、手段以及产生的不良后果，重点从公司治理、内部控制等角度分析导致控股股东资金占用行为发生的原因。案例旨在以加加食品为例，引导学员关注控股股东违规占用上市公司资金的动机、方式及后果，并思考与之相关的公司治理、内部控制等问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Jiajia food is a large seasoning food enterprise integrating production, R &amp; D and sales. In 2012, it landed in A-shares market and became the first listed company in China&#39;s condiment industry. However, after the listing, the controlling shareholders&#39; capital occupation occurred many times under the control of the actual controller, which led to the weak growth of the enterprise&#39;s performance. It also seriously damaged the corporate image, made the company punished by CSRC for many times, finally implemented other risk warning. This case is based on a number of incidents of controlling shareholders&#39; illegal occupation of funds after the listing of Jiajia Food as the main line, and describes in detail the motivation, means and adverse consequences of controlling shareholders&#39; infringement on the interests of listed companies, and also focuses on the analysis of the reasons for aggravating the capital occupation behavior of controlling shareholders from the perspective of corporate governance and internal control. The purpose of the case is to take Jiajia food as an example to guide trainees to focus on the motives, ways and consequences of controlling shareholders&#39; illegal occupation of funds of listed companies, and to think about the related issues such as corporate governance and internal control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《内部控制理论与实践》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司内部治理或内部控制对中小股东利益保护及其相关治理措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
